Following on from the success of Orion, Ares was brought to the world. Our first attempt at a First-Person Shooter,
we innovated in the space, migrating to the concept of a Second-Person Shooter (SPS) which was released to critical
acclaim. Known for it's "tomfoolery" and "complete RNG", Ares was an immediate hit and showed to the world the true
abilities of Nebula Forge.